Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:06.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:16.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:29.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:41.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:53.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:13.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:16.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:27.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:35.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:39.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:46.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:48.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:50.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:53.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:01.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:06.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:25.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:32.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to kick my butt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you heard me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But considering your level of strength,\Nyou couldn't even lay a hand on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brick Bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! He's blocking all of my punches.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Horo-Horo Chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop him, Kumacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with Perona-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:04:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea that stuffed animal\Nwas so nimble and powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here he can't even reach\Nthe zipper on his back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skip! Skip! Skip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your grubby hands off her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept your waiting,\NNami-san. Your knight is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a foul mood right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to deal with weaklings like--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Fur Face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absalom-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basses Côte!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you were in a foul mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't begin to describe mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so mad I feel like my body could explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:05:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And unfortunately for you, there is bad\Nblood between us over one other thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Clear-Clear History? Sanji's Stolen Dream"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:06:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Absalom-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... and I... have bad blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You are the man\Nwho stole one of my dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A dream...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't ring any bells.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some sort of misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...met for the first time today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to send you flying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with my Hands of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:07:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said to drop the bazookas\Nattached to your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I need to spell it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Nami-san gets hurt\Nbecause you went overboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one will be able to tell you were ever\Nalive by the time I'm through with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't possibly know\Nwhat I've got up my sleeves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said to lose the bazookas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! A bazooka magically materialized!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's about what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like the type of attack\Nyou would come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make yourself invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While in that state, you can make\Nanything you touch go invisible as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is your current ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Invisible man born of the Clear-Clear Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know every possible move you could make!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has that man met Absalom-sama\Nsomewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he know his powers inside and out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could this "bad blood" possibly be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back when I was a kid, I read an\Nencyclopedia on the Devil Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no interest in a shady object that\Nwould make the ocean grow to hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was one and one\Nalone that caught my interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that in the unlikely\Nevent I came across that Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would eat it, even if it meant\Nlosing the ability to swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there aren't two identical\NDevil Fruits at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ran into someone with that ability,\Nmy dream would go up in smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now do you get it? I wanted\Nto become an invisible man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said that you've\Ncrushed one of my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you ate the Clear-Clear Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's venting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put a lot of thought into my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ate the Fruit, I'd use my\Nabilities to watch women bathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Just think of all the things I could\Nuse it for. I could... watch women bathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Just imagine how I could help others.\NI could... watch women bathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you're really thinking about is\Nhow you could watch women bathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! After long years\Nof imagining what I'd do,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am fully aware of what I could see--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no, what I could accomplish with that ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Between this and endangering Nami-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have compounded\Ntransgression upon transgression,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,making it impossible to forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to wave goodbye to watching\Nwomen bathe--no, to your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what your problem was!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're picking a fight over the stupidest thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your complaint is beyond absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a freaking pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a point!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're equally bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have it your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will throw your sudden claim of\Nbad blood and rage right back at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lion muzzle wasn't my only transplant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elephant skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,300kg of compact bear and gorilla muscle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Hogback has conducted one\Ntransplant after the next on this body,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,allowing me to become the\Nultimate beastly masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Clear-Clear Fruit's ability is a mere bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:11:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next to my strength, it's nothing\Nmore than an accessory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still peeped!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a normal person kicked me,\Nmy body would break his leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's kicking me like I'm a normal man...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, I will be the last one laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have claimed the power you so desired!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the woman you longed to\Nprotect is about to become my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could not imagine a more bitter defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he abducted her,\NNami vanished with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost his trail after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna make Nami-san go invisible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:12:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't have her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wasting your energy!\NIt's time I showed you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the power of a Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? You're going to\Nsacrifice yourself for that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect her! Assuming you've got what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom Hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom Leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't drop that woman if I were you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Nami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped her! I guess you didn't\Nvalue her as much as your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't soil your pure\Nwhite dress with my blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn invisible man, sneaking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally over my dream now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if I can't turn invisible anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll peep without any special powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still going to peep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unhand me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not about to let go, you sick beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a mix of a bunch of animals,\NI bet you'll make lovely mincemeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extra Haché!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absalom-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A beast should be satisfied\Nwith watching women bathe--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scratch that! With a beastly bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ow, ow, ow! L-Let go!\N--Don't worry. They won't suck your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about\Nkicking my butt? What a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your lack of experience is going\Nto make you humiliate yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you underestimate others, greenhorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brick Bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow! Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:18:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk! Now I'm ticked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you jump over the rail?\NTrying to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.68,0:18:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Stamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that! So much for me not being\Nable to touch you, Giant Shallot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still in hot pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he was out of the picture,\NI could take down the other pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Mr. Negative Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still chasing after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he was out of the picture, I could\Ntake down that Horo-Horo Chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid bear zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Horo-Horo Chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away! Kumacy, hurry and finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo-Horo Chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare harm Perona-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close! Too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perona-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:21:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that stuffed animal\Nso freakishly strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this! Special Attack! Flame Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes, this is bad! It's fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked! It totally worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A zombie is still a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with this oil, I'll cast the\N"You Cannot Cross This Point" spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbbear! Now you can't come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes me invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't have to worry about you,\Nthat Horo-Horo Chick will be a pushover!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, like, rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:22:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I think I might teach\Nthat Horo-Horo Chick a lesson,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since she's weaker than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.71,0:22:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, Mr. Negative Nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could she be outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she couldn't be out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're up on a really high fl--whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dang! Why are you flying?!\NI thought you could only control ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What exactly is your power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate the power\Nof the Ghost Princess, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just figured out how I'm\Ngoing to take you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I knock you off,\Nthe others will be easy pickings!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec! This is not what I was expecting!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You haven't\Nlanded a single attack on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a sec! See, I can attack\Nby sniping, being negative,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bluffing, and, uh, using my 8,000 subordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm screwed! Why doesn't any\Nof it work on that Horo-Horo Chick?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.71,0:23:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Save Me, Hero!! My Enemy\NIs the Immortal Princess!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.98,0:23:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
